@page "/blog/second"
@{
    Page.Title = "Second post";
    Page.InFeed = true; //Requires a @page directive to be discovered
    Page.Published = "2025-07-02";
}

<Summary Render>
    Without inheriting the type @(nameof(BlogPost)) the following is needed to make it appear as a blog post:
</Summary>

<Markdown>

    - `@@page "/path"`
    - `Page.InFeed = true`

</Markdown>

 **Also notice** that any Markdown needs to be wrapped in @("<Markdown></Markdown>")